---
// Aboutセクション - スクロールアニメーション付き
---

<section id="about" class="about-section">
	<div class="about-container">
		<div class="about-header" data-animate="fade-up">
			<span class="section-label">About</span>
			<h2 class="section-title">Who I Am</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="about-content">
			<div class="about-text" data-animate="fade-up">
				<p>
					ソフトウェアエンジニアとして、美しく機能的なデジタル体験の創造に情熱を注いでいます。
				</p>
				<p>
					モダンなWeb技術に焦点を当て、パフォーマンスとアクセシビリティの両立を追求しています。
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="about-stats" data-animate="stagger">
				<div class="stat-item">
					<span class="stat-number">5+</span>
					<span class="stat-label">Years Experience</span>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-item">
					<span class="stat-number">50+</span>
					<span class="stat-label">Projects</span>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-item">
					<span class="stat-number">&infin;</span>
					<span class="stat-label">Curiosity</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about-section {
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 8rem 2rem;
		background: #fff;
	}

	.about-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.section-label {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.3em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #888;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		margin: 0 0 4rem;
		line-height: 1.1;
		color: #1a1a1a;
	}

	.about-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.about-text p {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		line-height: 2;
		color: #444;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.about-text p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.about-stats {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2.5rem;
	}

	.stat-item {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
		border-left: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
	}

	.stat-number {
		font-size: 3.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		color: #1a1a1a;
	}

	.stat-label {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: #666;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about-section {
			padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.about-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 3rem;
		}

		.about-stats {
			flex-direction: row;
			justify-content: space-between;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
		}

		.stat-item {
			flex: 1;
			min-width: 100px;
			padding-left: 1rem;
		}

		.stat-number {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.about-text p {
			font-size: 1.125rem;
		}
	}
</style>
